<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Performance Report - {{url}}</title>
<style>
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; background: #f0f2f5; color: #333; display: flex; min-height: 100vh; }
  .sidebar { width: 260px; background: #1a1d2e; color: #fff; padding: 32px 24px; position: fixed; height: 100vh; overflow-y: auto; }
  .sidebar h1 { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; color: #7c83fd; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .sidebar .subtitle { font-size: 12px; color: #8891a4; margin-bottom: 32px; }
  .sidebar .meta { font-size: 12px; color: #8891a4; line-height: 1.8; }
  .sidebar .meta strong { color: #c8cfdb; display: block; margin-top: 12px; }
  .sidebar .meta span { word-break: break-all; }
  .sidebar nav { margin-top: 32px; }
  .sidebar nav a { display: block; padding: 8px 12px; color: #8891a4; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .sidebar nav a:hover { background: #2d3148; color: #fff; }
  .main { margin-left: 260px; padding: 40px; width: calc(100% - 260px); }
  .header { background: #fff; border-radius: 12px; padding: 28px 32px; margin-bottom: 28px; box-shadow: 0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,.08); }
  .header h2 { font-size: 24px; color: #1a1d2e; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .header p { color: #666; font-size: 14px; }
  .section { background: #fff; border-radius: 12px; padding: 28px 32px; margin-bottom: 28px; box-shadow: 0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,.08); }
  .section h3 { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; color: #1a1d2e; margin-bottom: 20px; padding-bottom: 12px; border-bottom: 2px solid #f0f2f5; }
  table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 14px; }
  th { background: #f7f8fa; padding: 12px 16px; text-align: left; font-weight: 600; color: #555; border-bottom: 2px solid #e8eaed; }
  td { padding: 12px 16px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f2f5; }
  tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
  tr:hover td { background: #fafbfc; }
  .badge { display: inline-block; padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; }
  .good { color: #15803d; background: #dcfce7; }
  .warn { color: #92400e; background: #fef3c7; }
  .poor { color: #b91c1c; background: #fee2e2; }
  .score-big { font-size: 48px; font-weight: 900; }
  .score-row { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 32px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .score-card { background: #f7f8fa; border-radius: 10px; padding: 16px 24px; text-align: center; min-width: 120px; }
  .score-card .label { font-size: 11px; color: #888; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .05em; margin-top: 6px; }
  .info-box { background: #f0f4ff; border-left: 4px solid #6366f1; border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0; margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 13px; color: #444; line-height: 1.7; }
  .info-box summary { padding: 10px 18px; cursor: pointer; color: #3730a3; font-weight: 600; font-size: 13px; list-style: none; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; user-select: none; }
  .info-box summary::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }
  .info-box summary::before { content: '▶'; font-size: 10px; transition: transform .2s; display: inline-block; }
  .info-box[open] summary::before { transform: rotate(90deg); }
  .info-box-body { padding: 0 18px 14px 18px; }
  .info-box .method-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 12px; margin-top: 10px; }
  .info-box .method-item { background: #fff; border-radius: 6px; padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid #e0e7ff; }
  .info-box .method-item .method-name { font-weight: 700; color: #3730a3; font-size: 12px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .04em; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .info-box .method-item .method-desc { font-size: 12px; color: #555; line-height: 1.5; }
  .info-box .example { margin-top: 10px; background: #fff; border-radius: 6px; padding: 8px 12px; border: 1px solid #e0e7ff; font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 12px; color: #374151; }
  .tag { display: inline-block; background: #e0e7ff; color: #3730a3; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; margin-left: 8px; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="sidebar">
  <h1>⚡ PerfTest</h1>
  <div class="subtitle">Performance Benchmark</div>
  <div class="meta">
    <strong>URL</strong><span>{{url}}</span>
    <strong>Generated</strong><span>{{timestamp}}</span>
    <strong>Iterations</strong><span>{{iterations}}</span>
    <strong>Concurrency</strong><span>{{concurrency}}</span>
  </div>
  <nav>
    {{#if hasApi}}<a href="#api">📊 API Response Time</a>{{/if}}
    {{#if hasPage}}<a href="#page">🌐 Page Load Metrics</a>{{/if}}
    {{#if hasLighthouse}}<a href="#lighthouse">🔦 Lighthouse</a>{{/if}}
  </nav>
</div>
<div class="main">
  <div class="header">
    <h2>Performance Report</h2>
    <p>Benchmark results for <strong>{{url}}</strong> — {{timestamp}}</p>
  </div>

  {{#if hasApi}}
  <div class="section" id="api">
    <h3>📊 API Response Time <span class="tag">API</span></h3>
    <details class="info-box">
      <summary>ℹ How this is measured</summary>
      <div class="info-box-body">
      Each tool sends real HTTP GET requests to your URL and records the round-trip elapsed time from the moment the request is sent to when the full response is received — not including DNS or TCP setup for keep-alive connections.
      <div class="method-grid">
        <div class="method-item">
          <div class="method-name">Newman (Postman)</div>
          <div class="method-desc">Runs a generated Postman Collection sequentially for <em>N iterations</em>. Each request is timed using Newman's built-in execution engine, which wraps Node.js <code>http</code>/<code>https</code>. Reports min, avg, max, and P95 across all runs.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="method-item">
          <div class="method-name">JMeter</div>
          <div class="method-desc">Spins up <em>C virtual user threads</em>, each looping <em>N iterations</em>. Elapsed time is JMeter's <code>elapsed</code> column — time from request start to last byte of response. Enables true concurrency testing.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="example">Example ({{iterations}} iterations{{#if concurrency}}, {{concurrency}} threads{{/if}}): min=45ms · avg=120ms · max=310ms · P95=275ms · Success=100%</div>
      </div>
    </details>
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Tool</th><th>Min</th><th>Avg</th><th>Max</th><th>P95</th><th>Success%</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        {{#each apiResults}}
        <tr>
          <td><strong>{{tool}}</strong></td>
          <td>{{metrics.min}} ms</td>
          <td>{{metrics.avg}} ms</td>
          <td>{{metrics.max}} ms</td>
          <td>{{metrics.p95}} ms</td>
          <td>{{metrics.successRate}}%</td>
        </tr>
        {{/each}}
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>
  {{/if}}

  {{#if hasPage}}
  <div class="section" id="page">
    <h3>🌐 Page Load Metrics <span class="tag">PAGE</span></h3>
    <details class="info-box">
      <summary>ℹ How this is measured</summary>
      <div class="info-box-body">
      Both tools launch a real headless Chrome browser, navigate to your URL, and record browser-level timing events — not raw HTTP timings. This captures rendering, scripting, and resource loading exactly as a real user's browser would experience it.
      <div class="method-grid">
        <div class="method-item">
          <div class="method-name">Chrome DevTools (Puppeteer)</div>
          <div class="method-desc">Uses the <strong>Navigation Timing API</strong> (<code>window.performance.timing</code>) collected via Chrome DevTools Protocol.
            <br>• <strong>TTFB</strong> = <code>responseStart − navigationStart</code>
            <br>• <strong>DOM Load</strong> = <code>domContentLoadedEventEnd − navigationStart</code>
            <br>• <strong>Full Load</strong> = <code>loadEventEnd − navigationStart</code>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="method-item">
          <div class="method-name">Lighthouse</div>
          <div class="method-desc">Uses Chrome's built-in trace event profiler with Lighthouse's audit engine.
            <br>• <strong>LCP</strong> — largest above-fold element becomes visible
            <br>• <strong>FCP</strong> — first pixel of content painted
            <br>• <strong>TTI</strong> — page becomes fully interactive
            <br>• <strong>TBT</strong> — total thread-blocking time
            <br>• <strong>CLS</strong> — cumulative layout shift score
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="example">Example: TTFB=35ms · DOM Load=420ms · Full Load=850ms · LCP=1,200ms · CLS=0.02 (good)</div>
      </div>
    </details>
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Tool</th><th>TTFB</th><th>DOM Load</th><th>Full Load</th><th>FCP</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        {{#if hasDevtools}}
        <tr>
          <td><strong>{{devtools.tool}}</strong></td>
          <td>{{devtools.metrics.ttfb}} ms</td>
          <td>{{devtools.metrics.domLoad}} ms</td>
          <td>{{devtools.metrics.fullLoad}} ms</td>
          <td>{{devtools.metrics.fcp}} ms</td>
        </tr>
        {{/if}}
        {{#if hasLighthouse}}
        <tr>
          <td><strong>Lighthouse</strong></td>
          <td>—</td><td>—</td><td>—</td>
          <td>{{lighthouse.metrics.fcp}} ms</td>
        </tr>
        {{/if}}
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>
  {{/if}}

  {{#if hasLighthouse}}
  <div class="section" id="lighthouse">
    <h3>🔦 Lighthouse Performance <span class="tag">LIGHTHOUSE</span></h3>
    <div class="score-row" style="margin-bottom:24px;">
      <div class="score-card">
        <div class="score-big {{scoreColor lighthouse.metrics.performanceScore}}">{{lighthouse.metrics.performanceScore}}</div>
        <div class="label">Performance Score</div>
      </div>
      <div class="score-card">
        <div style="font-size:24px;font-weight:800;">{{lighthouse.metrics.lcp}} <small style="font-size:14px;">ms</small></div>
        <div class="label">LCP</div>
      </div>
      <div class="score-card">
        <div style="font-size:24px;font-weight:800;">{{lighthouse.metrics.fcp}} <small style="font-size:14px;">ms</small></div>
        <div class="label">FCP</div>
      </div>
      <div class="score-card">
        <div style="font-size:24px;font-weight:800;">{{lighthouse.metrics.tti}} <small style="font-size:14px;">ms</small></div>
        <div class="label">TTI</div>
      </div>
      <div class="score-card">
        <div style="font-size:24px;font-weight:800;">{{lighthouse.metrics.tbt}} <small style="font-size:14px;">ms</small></div>
        <div class="label">TBT</div>
      </div>
      <div class="score-card">
        <div style="font-size:24px;font-weight:800;">{{fixed lighthouse.metrics.cls 3}}</div>
        <div class="label">CLS</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  {{/if}}

  {{#if hasSkipped}}
  <div class="section">
    <h3>⚠ Skipped / Errors</h3>
    {{#each skipped}}
    <div class="skipped">{{tool}}: {{reason}}{{error}}</div>
    {{/each}}
  </div>
  {{/if}}
</div>
</body>
</html>
